review_text: OK quality dimsum. You can get discount offers if you arrive before 11:00. Don't expect steaming carts pushed between tables like in the South. Dining in the room will charge extra.

There are a few Tang Gong seafood in Beijing, this one is at Chongwen Men, parking is pretty easy along the road. You don't need to worry about anything there,food is good,makes you believe the chefs behind the grant hall making lovely dishes with heart and soul.
